Class Tile

java.lang.Object
Tile
public class Tile extends Object
This class contains conditions of a certain tile in the farm. It helps determine the conditions of the certain crop (if the crop is watered, fertilized enough, harvested in the right time).

    • updateWithered

      public void updateWithered()
      This method updates if the plant currently on the tile is withered. A plant is withered if it has not been watered and fertilized enough on the day of harvest or if the day of harvest has passed.
